obile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2530090\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 13, 2022</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104mut1665702921504.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/mut1665702921504.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/mut1665702921504.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"mut1665702921504\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Identify and Prioritize User Views\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">A user view comprises the data needed for a business activity. The data can come from more than one modeled entity. Do not confuse the user view with the user interface of the application.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mut1665702921504__p_d45704e1_d45705e1_d45706e1\">It is not feasible to analyze all user views because it would be too time-consuming and probably not worth the effort. User views that are candidates for further examination have the following characteristics:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mut1665702921504__li_d22814e1_d22815e1_d22816e1\">Crucial to the business\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mut1665702921504__li_d22817e1_d22818e1_d22819e1\">Have strict performance requirements\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mut1665702921504__li_d22820e1_d22821e1_d22822e1\">Imply processing of high volumes\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mut1665702921504__li_d22823e1_d22824e1_d22825e1\">Are needed frequently\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mut1665702921504__li_d22826e1_d22827e1_d22828e1\">Comprise many entities (more than an average number)\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mut1665702921504__li_d22829e1_d22830e1_d22831e1\">Are accessed by many components (more than an average number)\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mut1665702921504__li_d22832e1_d22833e1_d22834e1\">Combine several application models\n </li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mut1665702921504__p_d45707e1_d45708e1_d45709e1\">For each user view that needs further examination, ensure that you have a good description of the user view, including the data needed and the objects accessed. It should provide enough information so that you can:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mut1665702921504__li_d22835e1_d22836e1_d22837e1\">Identify the need for access path analysis\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mut1665702921504__li_d22838e1_d22839e1_d22840e1\">Identify access profiles. The access profile is the sequence of all access paths needed by a user view.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mut1665702921504__li_d22841e1_d22842e1_d22843e1\">Determine the moment of access of the access objects and estimate or calculate the access frequency\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mut1665702921504__li_d22844e1_d22845e1_d22846e1\">Understand the impact on the implementation\n </li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mut1665702921504__p_d45710e1_d45711e1_d45712e1\">The information can be provided by a use case that describes the relevant business activity, including the interaction diagrams. Useful information can include:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mut1665702921504__li_d22847e1_d22848e1_d22849e1\">User view name (use case name)\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mut1665702921504__li_d22850e1_d22851e1_d22852e1\">Purpose, indicating the functionality (use case activity)\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mut1665702921504__li_d22853e1_d22854e1_d22855e1\">Actors interacting with the user view\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mut1665702921504__li_d22856e1_d22857e1_d22858e1\">Type of interaction; for example, maintenance vs. data retrieval, performing calculations vs. producing a report, or a possible combination of these\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mut1665702921504__li_d22859e1_d22860e1_d22861e1\">Importance from a business point of view\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mut1665702921504__li_d22862e1_d22863e1_d22864e1\">Response time requirements\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mut1665702921504__li_d22865e1_d22866e1_d22867e1\">Indication of the volumes processed\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mut1665702921504__li_d22868e1_d22869e1_d22870e1\">Frequency of use\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mut1665702921504__li_d22871e1_d22872e1_d22873e1\">Application models and entities accessed\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mut1665702921504__li_d22874e1_d22875e1_d22876e1\">Security aspects\n </li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530090\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530090\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Identify and Prioritize User Views Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 13, 2022 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Identify and Prioritize User Views A user view comprises the data needed for a business activity. The data can come from more than one modeled entity. Do not confuse the user view with the user interface of the application. It is not feasible to analyze all user views because it would be too time-consuming and probably not worth the effort. User views that are candidates for further examination have the following characteristics: Crucial to the business Have strict performance requirements Imply processing of high volumes Are needed frequently Comprise many entities (more than an average number) Are accessed by many components (more than an average number) Combine several application models For each user view that needs further examination, ensure that you have a good description of the user view, including the data needed and the objects accessed. It should provide enough information so that you can: Identify the need for access path analysis Identify access profiles. The access profile is the sequence of all access paths needed by a user view. Determine the moment of access of the access objects and estimate or calculate the access frequency Understand the impact on the implementation The information can be provided by a use case that describes the relevant business activity, including the interaction diagrams. Useful information can include: User view name (use case name) Purpose, indicating the functionality (use case activity) Actors interacting with the user view Type of interaction; for example, maintenance vs. data retrieval, performing calculations vs. producing a report, or a possible combination of these Importance from a business point of view Response time requirements Indication of the volumes processed Frequency of use Application models and entities accessed Security aspects Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}